title: Dallas 10x19 High Noon for Calhoun.avi
description:
Yes boys and girls: DALLAS is back, and now that the dream is over, its even better than ever!

J.R. and Bobby take their families to California in attempt to avoid Calhoun's wrath; Cliff's risky deal with Jeremy Wendell continues; Donna is courted further by Senator Dowling; Miss Ellie and Clayton begin to reconnect.

First Aired: 2/06/1987

Priscilla Presley (Jenna) is not present in this episode.
